name: 2022 10th International Conference on Intelligent Computing and Wireless Optical Communications
content: Publication: Submitted paper will be peer reviewed by conference committees. Accepted papers will be included in ICWOC 2022 Conference Proceedings, which will be archived in IEEE Xplore , and indexed by EI Compendex, Scopus, and other indexing services. ICWOC 2022 is listed in IEEE Official Conference Calendar: https://conferences.ieee.org/conferences\_events/conferences/conferencedetails/55996
